  "detailed_description": "When Maria, a globe-trotting antique restorer, arrives in the sun-soaked town of Bellariva, she has no idea just how broken it will turn out to be. She wants nothing more than to help the town’s inhabitants save their most beloved possessions, but when it’s their personal lives that are starting to fracture, she’ll need to find a way to hold them together, one spare screw at a time.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1202900/extras/43029298c76a34dce3c32a50da61b005.poster.avif?t=1762967969\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1202900/extras/43029298c76a34dce3c32a50da61b005.webm?t=1762967969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>Figure out the inner workings of the objects brought to Maria and find a way to fix them.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1202900/extras/2a3cb6b44989db378184507bc452b1d2.poster.avif?t=1762967969\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1202900/extras/2a3cb6b44989db378184507bc452b1d2.webm?t=1762967969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1202900/extras/2a3cb6b44989db378184507bc452b1d2.mp4?t=1762967969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1202900/extras/9ab0b7ca9f7e42c0b5db16439dfa66b3.avif?t=1762967969\" width=600 height=208 /></span><br><strong>Meet the townsfolk of Bellariva. Come to love their quirks and help them reconnect.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video